

Simplified simulation of high-energy particle storms

2023 Ernst Nordstrom Cederholm, Lukas Bahner.
Marcial Sanchis Agudo 

This report describes our work on the project of the PDC Summer School 2023. It is part of the course
”FDD3260 High-performance Computing for Computational Scientists 5.0 credits” offered at KTH Royal
Institute of Technology in Stockholm. The code in energy_storms.c has been parallelized using mpi, omp and cuda. 

--------------------------------------------------------------
How to run the code
--------------------------------------------------------------
Exampel run in bash:

$ make clean
$ make all
$ ./energy_storms_omp 20 test_files/test_05_a20_p4_w1


To see a description of the Makefile options execute:
$ make help 

Use the input files in the test_files directory for your tests.
